  id: SimonsMorse
  title: Simon s'Morse
  author: PossessedHood416
  description: "\u201CJust think about it Simon. In just a few hours, you and I will
    be sitting around a campfire making delicious hot schmoes.\u201D\r\n\u201CThey\u2019re
    called s\u2019mores, Tasha.\u201D\r\n\nColab with RazorBlade_Wolfe!\n\nHelp Simon
    toast the perfect marshmellow by inputting morse into some logs.\n\nThe manual
    can be found in the manuals folder of the game or at ktane.timwi.de.\n\r\nContact
    PossessedHood416 or RazorBlade_Wolfe on Discord if there are any bugs."
